2013-06-11  Alberto Otero de la Roza  <aoterodelaroza@ucmerced.edu>

	* test/cryst/xrd2/testme.m: fixed for the new xrd syntax.

	* src/cr_unitcell.m: now it is possible to represent more than one
	cell. Fixed some tests to incorporate this change.

	* src/mol_polyhedron.m: added. Builds polyhedra from a molecular
	description.

	* src/mol_stick.m: only build rcov matrix if dist(1)<0.

	* test/other/texture_catalog/testme.m: added. Script to generate
	the texture catalog for povray.

	* src/rep_write_pov.m: modified to respect texture preferences on
	color and transparency. Removed #includes.

	* src/rep_texdbstart.m: basic set of textures, with 'string' and
	'pigment'. The texture can give the colors as %.4f in which case
	the colors from the rgb of the elements are used or enforce some
	color. The transparency can also be forced by the texture.

	* src/rep_addlight.m: changed White to 'rgb 1' to avoid using
	colors.inc in pov.

	* test/mol/water_hexamers/testme.m,
	test/mol/grapheneslide/testme.m,
	test/cryst/cam_electride/testme.m, test/mol/gold/testme.m: fixed
	the modelview matrix to use the default center of projection.

	* src/rep_addcamera_modelview.m: the elements (1:3,4) of the
	modelview matrix are the cop. Elements (4,1:3) are the camera
	translation. Elements (1:3,1:3) are the rotation. If the r passed
	to set_repdefaultscene is 4x3 instead of 4x4 then the default cop
	is used (the barycenter of the balls in the representation).

	* src/rep_texture.m: do not crash if texture is not found. Go back
	to default.

	* src/rep_texdbstart.m: improved arrangement of texture db in the
	routine. Set a default for pov and obj.

